root: ^How many years did I get to live without restarting? 16? 17 …
^I met Sachi and my memories of her came rushing back to me.
^She couldn’t forget the feeling of me.
^Even though we had never met... I don’t understand how it could even be possible but what’s the point in thinking about it now.
^Here I am back again… in 2018. My first year of high school.
